<taxonomicName authority="Desmarest, 1818" authorityName="Desmarest" authorityYear="1818" box="[323,808,2806,2835]" class="Mammalia" family="Noctilionidae" genus="Noctilio" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="411" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="albiventris">Noctilio albiventris Desmarest, 1818</taxonomicName>
, 
<materialsCitation pageId="3" pageNumber="411">
“I’Amérique méridionale.” Restricted by A. Cabrera in 1958 to Rio Sao Francisco, 
<collectingRegion box="[770,851,2850,2875]" country="Brazil" name="Bahia" pageId="3" pageNumber="411">Bahia</collectingRegion>
